I added the linear sweep to #12, but now the audio is screwy, and I'm not 
sure why, but it's the guys with their "girl comments"--the usual 
embarrassing comments, but that's what they claim to see from their side. 
Guess it's at least unique for EVP contacts, and what am I supposed to do, 
not share what I get?  Sometimes when the box isn't working right the voices 
come through better, maybe?
The audio is like somekind of feedback.

Frank-S
